description: Nearly 40 years in Eugene have taught the folks at Ritta's Burritos to a lot, and they've taken those lessons to the streets of Oregon! This beautiful food trailer is serving quality burritos, bowls, and more right to you! A regular at Eugene's Saturday Market for years, Ritta's is a real tradition of the community, so come and taste some of the city's most delicious history!
name: Ritta's Burritos
